{"tid":2363687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教禁「香港人加油」年曆卡稱威脅人身安全　邵家臻斥針對政治犯僭建規則","createTime":"2021-01-12T11:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T23:25:07.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95839164705030e2a2cd4bb6d509cd292f2c8abf","tid":2363687,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9K6i_Xm8j7zVdrRfW7hjsBy3LPs=/673x708/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5SPQU2VZFFZFKXXY37XSWGLX4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9K6i_Xm8j7zVdrRfW7hjsBy3LPs%3D%2F673x708%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5SPQU2VZFFZFKXXY37XSWGLX4.JPG&h=0963ff10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邵家臻fb專頁截圖<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n寄入監獄的信在送抵在囚人士手上前，都必經懲教署人員拆開檢閱，早前「612人道支援基金」的年報便曾遭署方扣起。事隔3個月，有囚權組織寄出的年曆卡及回條，被懲教署以威脅人身安全及監獄保安為由再退回。囚權組織「石牆花」創辦人邵家臻指，無法理解年曆卡及回條如何威脅監獄保安，批評懲教署不斷僭建規則，禁絕政治犯可收取的書信。<br />\n囚權組織「石牆花」以及每日寄出新聞、討論區貼文予在囚人士的組織「解悶工廠」，早前寄出的2021年曆卡及「和你送年糕」活動回條，被懲教署引用《監獄規則》退回信件。邵家臻指年曆上完全沒有敏感資料，而另一份寄予130名在囚人士的回條，亦只是詢問他們是否有興趣透過組織，送年糕或花給家人，過去亦已舉辦過類似活動，但今次活動回條卻遭退回。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210112/YSHKRO4C3RFAHGV2EQWUZXHGBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210112%2FYSHKRO4C3RFAHGV2EQWUZXHGBU%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuSBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=b536d9ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210112%2FYSHKRO4C3RFAHGV2EQWUZXHGBU%2F&h=cefad57f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210112/YSHKRO4C3RFAHGV2EQWUZXHGBU/</a>"},{"pid":"1a3009b2b5f334efdc12d71e1581745fd32e2e31","tid":2363687,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"15e9da1189d7a01dc5e6ea60a1e05d44444fe1e9","tid":